      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# New Features & Updates  \r\n\r\n### Improved Form Options  \r\nWe've added new form types to provide more flexibility:  \r\n- **Dropdown (Single Choice)** – Users can select one option from a predefined list.  \r\n- **Checkboxes (Multiple Choice)** – Allow multiple selections when needed.  \r\n- **Title & Description Fields** – Add context for a clearer and more structured form experience.  \r\n\r\n### Light & Dark Mode Themes  \r\nA new **light and dark mode** option is now available, letting you choose the appearance that works best for you.  \r\n\r\n### Payment Plan Update  \r\n- You can publish **one form for free** under the Free Plan.  \r\n- For additional forms, choose between **$6 per year** or a **one-time $10 lifetime deal**.  \r\n\r\nThese updates aim to make form creation more flexible and accessible.  \r\n",
